{
  "stem": "27351.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had a little girl, a four-year-old child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He gave us the kitchen, and we-- we were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He started to work in so-called mobel lager, which was a large warehouse of furniture run by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I understand that they were taking Jewish furniture, renewing them, collecting, repairing them, and sending them off to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was coming home very, very tired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember once seeing-- in this small kitchen, we-- there was only a place for one bed, and then a cot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was put up only in the evening for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And around 8 o'clock, after eating our soup-- or maybe it was 7 o'clock in the evening-- we all went to bed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then a friend of Henryk came just to visit with his school friend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was from a rich family, a very nice boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he looked at-- in this scene, then he sat down on my brother's cot and asked him to whistle something for him, because Henryk whistled beautifully.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I remember this whistling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He whistled the 'Eine Kleine Nachtmuzik' by Mozart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we all cried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Well, we were poor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I started to do something, and I don't remember exactly what, but I remember cleaning some place where children played during the day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a sort of a communal kindergarten or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I would wash the floors there, but I don't remember very much of that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Well, this is how life was going on until September, 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And September, 1942, on the 22nd of September, the so-called Big Action started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But on the 21st of September, my brother came from work and told us to come with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
